{"tid":2194791,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"高盛重申看淡蘋果 料再跌3成至80美元","createTime":"2020-09-08T17:32:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T18:22:10.000Z","uid":66271,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"02ddfa52396b3e881c6517f34e48eb758ed9530c","tid":2194791,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T17:32:22.000Z","msg":"美國科技股今晚再下跌，投行高盛表示，看淡蘋果的股價，認為未來增長前景不足以支持其高估值，重申其對蘋果「沽售」的評級，及80美元的目標價，即較現價再跌約3成。<br />\n<br />\n彭博引述高盛分析師Rod Hall表示，iPhone的增長面對困難，而蘋果的服務及可穿戴業務之規模不足以使公司恢復增長。目前蘋果2021年預測市盈率，與Google母公司Alphabet、微軟及Facebook等相若，但該行預期，蘋果在2021年度的盈收會令市場失望，不足以支持這高估值。<br />\n<br />\n高盛自4月以來已把蘋果列入沽售評級，然而4月起蘋果股價一度急升6成，不過自本月初的高位以來，蘋果已累跌逾一成。目前報115.94美元，跌4.15%。"},{"pid":"144bd909e59042ef46f1c243b9d759d1898091d7","tid":2194791,"uid":122906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T17:34:04.000Z","msg":"快<br />\n利伸 未買"},{"pid":"1bbd5acda704dd899110ab6921903638264b407a","tid":2194791,"uid":76747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T17:35:09.000Z","msg":"連燈大行向高盛表示<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20aecaa2496bb7289a28db500941108de7ad881e","tid":2194791,"uid":236002,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T17:36:25.000Z","msg":"多謝燈神，依家買"},{"pid":"cf6a2439392a80b67497fce187c67d0e048f6030","tid":2194791,"uid":330457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T17:39:20.000Z","msg":"所以Tesla幾時肯落50"},{"pid":"8dea7cfd616d1c2048839b05417d5d95e64d0e8f","tid":2194791,"uid":62749,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T17:42:32.000Z","msg":"拆股後80蚊<br />\n等同之前320<br />\n武肺前高位都係咁上下<br />\n高盛唔算估到好低"},{"pid":"0d244e3f387975fb61b37e8d0dbd5da665df312d","tid":2194791,"uid":6297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T17:43:29.000Z","msg":"由4月錯到9月話